title: 820-01987: Need help identifying two missing components
message: This board came with no power. Noticed it's missing D3312 and D3328. Could these two be possibly causing my no power issue and if so, does anyone know what the part description is so that i can order them?

title: 820-01987: Need help identifying two missing components
message:
These protection diodes can't stop the board to work; if missing, of course.
Farnell sells them:
[URL unfurl="true"]https://es.farnell.com/c/proteccion-de-circuitos/elementos-de-proteccion-esd?encapsulado-del-diodo=x3dfn2[/URL]
